{"tid":503564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫客申信用卡　死者花百萬買療程","createTime":"2017-12-19T03:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T07:57:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9575a610e3e361a845f4b2e3ff2d53cd9ba074d2","tid":503564,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20249067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20249067&d=yxQoWzmCNdQRN7MG33MByzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6b02e863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20249067&h=a55db885\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20249067</a><br />\n<br />\n幫客申信用卡　死者花百萬買療程<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171219/large/19la5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F19la5p4.jpg&h=70ff093a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王靜波因DR毒針療程而需截去一雙小腿和四隻手指。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】法官張慧玲昨指本案其中一個加刑因素是DR的推銷手法駭人聽聞，包括佣金制度、為客人申請信用卡等，可謂完全不負責任，從三名事主購買CIK的情況可見一斑。死者陳宛琳生前與丈夫經營茶餐廳，屬小康之家，丈夫透露支票簿顯示妻子曾在DR花過百萬元；至於對美容療程不感興趣的事主王靜波，則錯信職員CIK可增強抵抗力，一心求健康卻換來截肢下場。<br />\n<br />\n前教師： 𠵱家係廢人<br />\n<br />\n在事故中截去一雙小腿和四隻手指的前小學教師王靜波（65歲），她早前供稱自2008年起便定期在DR做美容，DR時常向她推銷不同療程但都被她拒絕，唯一例外便是涉案的CIK療程。王指鑑於家庭負擔甚重，既要照顧患自閉的智障兒子又要供樓，另一名兒子又失業，導致身心疲累，望CIK可改善精神狀態，換取健康體魄。她作供期間一度情緒失控，哭着說：「我需要健康，𠵱家完全廢人一個！」<br />\n<br />\n另任職校工、月入僅7,000元的事主黃鳳群（62歲）則透露，自09年起每月在DR做美容或淋巴推拿，還做過幹細胞療程。DR職員於2012年向她推銷CIK，聲稱可提升免疫力，又謂原價18萬元，但獨家給她逾半價優惠，黃終花7萬元買療程。她用現金1萬元加上兩張信用卡各3萬元分期付款，DR職員一度提出幫她申請新信用卡但遭她拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊思雅、勞東來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t呈64求情信　退款單　求減刑<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\tDR毒針案 　推銷手法「駭人聽聞」官斥無悔意兼卸責　周向榮囚12年<br />\n要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"02db13827aa2ff575bd5bf1954652fb13e71df9c","tid":503564,"uid":154702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"抵個老闆入去坐"},{"pid":"d44480b85fa002c07897d26fb5463b9494794ce6","tid":503564,"uid":9286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"12年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde5889d7c7bcbcfc0d8a127bbb92e43ba4eae1c","tid":503564,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人錢易搵"},{"pid":"7d94cd87cd070c0a269324465d86d8aef511aa6b","tid":503564,"uid":65598,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人錢易搵</blockquote><br />\n易搵還易搵<br />\n你可以標高價錢氹班女人買你服務產品<br />\n但唔係咁樣害鳩人，咁同大陸有咩分別？"},{"pid":"66b56c4a7698c94eeb0028bf9f256d96725c45e3","tid":503564,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"f567e056b9d650b2073b301b2bafd15160bae73b","tid":503564,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nShow Blocked User"},{"pid":"ba797841f3dd7e7162aedcac7dd9a1b3c18aa984","tid":503564,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現在不是騙錢是殺人<br />\n唔驗有沒有菌就注射入身體"},{"pid":"4ba7a1153835bc6eeaf9f81a084e98105ac8bbc9","tid":503564,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人錢易搵</blockquote><br />\n易搵還易搵<br />\n你可以標高價錢氹班女人買你服務產品<br />\n但唔係咁樣害鳩人，咁同大陸有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n都唔第一日<br />\n<br />\nd美容、年輕產品求奇加個科技形容詞（紅外線、磁力、幹細胞、細胞重組）d女人就會狗沖<br />\n全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間美容院白鳩痴，冇料到亂咁打野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次冇料打生理鹽水就算啦，隨時安慰劑效應仲大，個客話唔定會返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945da55f972117f24dec55cd14bea40e573695cb","tid":503564,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"海關消委會警察呢？唔死人就唔查"},{"pid":"30298b48a49ea561ed9809e57f5fb0d96d1189b0","tid":503564,"uid":114084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人錢易搵</blockquote><br />\n易搵還易搵<br />\n你可以標高價錢氹班女人買你服務產品<br />\n但唔係咁樣害鳩人，咁同大陸有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n都唔第一日<br />\n<br />\nd美容、年輕產品求奇加個科技形容詞（紅外線、磁力、幹細胞、<span style=\"color: red;\">細胞重組</span>）d女人就會狗沖<br />\n全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間美容院白鳩痴，冇料到亂咁打野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次冇料打生理鹽水就算啦，隨時安慰劑效應仲大，個客話唔定會返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有電流推動同磁場轉動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}